rows.label: tlk70000032_03_msg0001
rows.name:
Congratulations, Laura-sama!
The knighting ceremony was a sight
to behold

rows.label: tlk70000032_03_msg0002
rows.name:
Actually, to tell you the truth, I didn't
see it. The doctor had me cooped up
for observation.

rows.label: tlk70000032_03_msg0003
rows.name:
But Nittle and Bry told me all
about it in such great detail I
felt like I was there!

rows.label: tlk70000032_03_msg0004
rows.name:
Meeting Laura-sama and seeing how
proud you all are has made me forget
my injuries for a moment.

rows.label: tlk70000032_03_msg0005
rows.name: Iira thanks you for your service!
